</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Check that voltage varies depending on throttle opening angle as following graph while throttle valve is opened and closed manually.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I8C50B130004.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "37.731mm" ver = "01" gw = "203" gh = "90"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
